Package de.braintags.io.vertx.pojomapper.init

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDataStoreInit
    Implementations of IDataStoreInit are used to initialize an IDataStore by defined DataStoreSettings
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDataStoreInit
    Abstract implementation of IDataStoreInit
    DataStoreSettings
    Preferences to initialize an IDataStore By using this defintion you are able to instantiate an instance of IDataStoreInit defined by DataStoreSettings.getDatastoreInit() and instantiate an IDataStore by using the Properties inside the current class
    EncoderSettings
    EncoderSettings defines the properties of an IEncoder, which shall be used by the current application.
